title: [bzoing] Better Living Through Circuitry
description:
A Digital Odyssey into the Electronic Dance Culture of the 90's.


Director: Jon Reiss

Genre: Documentary, Music

Year: 1999

Cast: Moby, Lords of Acid, Roni Size, Frankie Bones, Meat Beat Manifesto, Adam X, DJ Spooky, Juno Reactor, System 7, Genesis P. Orridge, Carl Cox, Loop Guru, among others...

Video: AVI, 24bit, 512x384p, 29fps, DivX
Audio: MP3, 128kbps
Runtime: 85 mins.
